text: With all of the wonder, adventure and thrills synonymous with one of the most popular and successful franchises in cinema history, this all-new motion-picture event sees the return of favorite characters and dinosaurs--along with new breeds more awe-inspiring and terrifying than ever before. Welcome to JURASSIC WORLD: FALLEN KINGDOM.
